{
  "stem": "20035.5",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I mean, that was machine gun, automatic.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But even the end of the line sometimes they just pushed a couple of machine guns that they should move faster.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I mean, it's easier for them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They were bicycles and motorcycles and cars and trucks.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And they had-- they were-- they had the physical strength to do it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We didn't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And If it wouldn't have been from-- for the support and help and for the more than support of my brother, physical support of my brother, I don't thinks I would have made it.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "By that time already, I was weak and sick.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And finally we arrived to a camp called Ravensbruck, R-A-V-E-N-S-- V-E-N-S-B-R-U-C-K.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Germany.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was still in Germany, some-- somewhere near-- near the northern part of-- of Germany.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Ravensbruck, we probably stayed there a week doing absolutely nothing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, maybe the only advantage was that at least we had somewhere shelter over our head into a barrack or somewhere where we were able to-- to sleep.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But back to the routine of the appeal and counting and god knows how-- how-- how small and how wonderful that that so-called shelter was.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But at least there was something there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And from there, within a short while, probably a week after, they started to march us again.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we marched.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we arrived to a place called Neubrandenburg, N-E-A-- yeah.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "N-E-A-U-B-R-U-D-E-N-B-R-G.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I had to think about.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That's also in Germany, by the way.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And this-- this is also the northern part of Germany, where Neubrandenburg, there was some kind of-- some kind of barracks.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But I really honestly don't even remember it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Neubrandenburg, my memory is already extremely vague.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I had-- had a stomach typhoid, dysentery, and really the end of my life.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
